msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for Employers to add multi-departments related to jobs. Job seeker can apply to jobs related to the desired department."
msgstr "WP Job Portal offers isang feature para sa mga employer sa magdagdag multi-mga departamento kaugnay sa jobs. naghahanap ng trabaho maaaring apply sa jobs kaugnay sa ang desired departamento."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for employers to make folders. Employers can make a folder and copy their resumes into the folders."
msgstr "WP Job Portal offers isang feature para sa mga employer sa make mga folder. mga employer maaaring make isang folder at copy their mga resume into ang mga folder."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for employers to perform some actions on resumes. Employers have some rights to reject or accept the job seeker resume."
msgstr "WP Job Portal offers isang feature para sa mga employer sa perform some actions sa mga resume. mga employer have some rights sa tanggihan o accept ang naghahanap ng trabaho resume."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for making the jobs as Featured Job. This will help to make it easier for job seekers to find jobs."
msgstr "WP Job Portal offers isang feature para sa making ang jobs bilang featured na trabaho. This ay help sa make it easier para sa mga naghahanap ng trabaho sa find jobs."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for searching the jobs by tags. Employers will add some tags related to jobs search."
msgstr "WP Job Portal offers isang feature para sa searching ang jobs ng mga tag. mga employer ay magdagdag some mga tag kaugnay sa jobs paghahanap."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for the job seeker to add their multi-resume. Job seeker will be able to create a multiple resume for applying any job."
msgstr "WP Job Portal offers isang feature para sa ang naghahanap ng trabaho sa magdagdag their multi-resume. naghahanap ng trabaho ay be able sa gumawa isang multiple resume para sa applying any job."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for users to see address data for states, cities or both. Admin will upload that file."
msgstr "WP Job Portal offers isang feature para sa mga user sa see address data para sa mga estado, mga lungsod o both. admin ay upload that file."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for visitors. A visitor can apply to any company posted jobs. The visitor will apply for the jobs by their resume."
msgstr "WP Job Portal offers isang feature para sa mga bisita. isang bisita maaaring apply sa any kompanya posted jobs. ang bisita ay apply para sa ang jobs ng their resume."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature in which Employer and Job Seekers can share and tell their friends about Jobs by sending them an email."
msgstr "Nag-aalok ang WP Job Portal ng feature kung saan maaaring i-share ng mga employer at naghahanap ng trabaho ang mga trabaho sa kanilang mga kaibigan sa pamamagitan ng email."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a jobs share feature on various social media sites for Employers and Job Seekers."
msgstr "Nag-aalok ang WP Job Portal ng job sharing feature sa iba't ibang social media site para sa mga employer at naghahanap ng trabaho."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a Resume and print feature. Employer and Job Seeker can view the Resume page or take a print of the Resume."
msgstr "WP Job Portal offers isang resume at print feature. employer at naghahanap ng trabaho maaaring tingnan ang resume pahina o take isang print ng ang resume."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers an outstanding feature for employers to featured their companies. Employers will be able to featured their desired companies."
msgstr "Nag-aalok ang WP Job Portal ng feature para gawing featured ng mga employer ang kanilang mga napiling kompanya."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers multiple reports by jobs, by companies and by resume. Admin can see overall reports of Employer and Job Seeker."
msgstr "Nag-aalok ang WP Job Portal ng maraming ulat ayon sa trabaho, kompanya, at resume. Makikita ng admin ang kabuuang ulat ng employer at naghahanap ng trabaho."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers Real Simple Syndication (RSS) to set feeds for the jobs. Admin manipulates RSS settings. Employers and Job Seekers can see the Jobs RSS."
msgstr "WP Job Portal offers Real Simple Syndication (RSS) sa set mga feed para sa ang jobs. admin manipulates RSS mga setting. mga employer at mga naghahanap ng trabaho maaaring see ang Jobs RSS."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers timely customer support. If you have any queries, we're here to help you every step of the way."
msgstr "WP Job Portal offers timely customer support. kung you have any queries, we're dito sa help you every step ng ang way."

